data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in the desirable Edgewater neighborhood. This newly constructed property, built in 2021, has only been lived in for approximately 6 months, ensuring its pristine condition. Upon entering, you will be greeted by the elegance of hardwood floors that flow gracefully throughout the main living area, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The upgraded kitchen is a true highlight, boasting stainless steel appliances that elevate the overall aesthetic. With an island featuring seating, meal preparation and entertaining become a joyous affair. The large open layout of this home accentuates its spaciousness and provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Abundant natural lighting fills the living spaces, creating a bright and airy ambiance that adds to the overall charm of this property. The bedrooms, each carpeted for comfort, are designed to be cozy retreats. Generously sized closets ensure there is plenty of storage space for all your belongings. The backyard is spacious, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities with friends or creating your own private oasis. The potential is endless when it comes to designing your dream outdoor space. Don't miss this opportunity to own a contemporary, thoughtfully designed home in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in Blue Springs! This home has an assumable FHA loan at a low rate for qualified buyers.
